## Output configs
set $laptop eDP-1
bindswitch --reload --locked lid:on output $laptop disable
bindswitch --reload --locked lid:off output $laptop enable

## Input configs
input "type:touchpad" {
  natural_scroll enabled
  tap enabled
  click_method clickfinger
}

input type:keyboard {
    xkb_layout us
    xkb_options caps:super
}

